A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing March 20, 2025, as Buc-ee's Day at the state capitol and celebrating Buc-ee's
2 and its presence in Georgia; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Buc-ee's is a chain of travel centers known for its award-winning clean
4 restrooms and abundant fuel pumps including diesel exhaust fluid, ethanol free fuel, and EV
5 charging stations; and
6 WHEREAS, Buc-ee's offers a variety of merchandise, from clever and quirky, such as
7 Buc-ee the Beaver inflatables with interchangeable party signs and Buc-ee's onesies for
8 babies and adults, to conventional and sophisticated, such as cast-iron skillets, specialty
9 wood cutting boards, and gold and silver jewelry; and
10 WHEREAS, Buc-ee's is especially known for its extensive assortment of drinks and food,
11 including but not limited to Beaver Nuggets, in-house made fudge, a wall covered end-to-end
12 with a variety of different flavored beef jerkies, and "fresh brisket on the board" that is
13 smoked in house and made into deliciously warm ready-to-eat sandwiches; and
